&lt;p&gt;Company: Forgent AI&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Location: Berlin (Hybrid)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Type: Full-time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start: ASAP&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Forgent AI&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Europe&#39;s public sector spends €2.4 trillion a year, but the best companies can&#39;t compete because they&#39;re drowning in paperwork. Forgent AI builds domain-specific AI agents that automate the entire tendering process, from discovery to proposal generation to compliance, cutting manual effort by ~80%. We&#39;ve onboarded 40+ organisations in under a year, we&#39;re backed by Cherry Ventures and angels from OpenAI, Anthropic, and DeepMind, and we&#39;re scaling fast from Germany into Europe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Forgent AI’s first Customer Success hire, you’ll own the post-sale customer journey end-to-end: onboarding, adoption, value realization, renewals/expansion, and turning early customers into referenceable champions. You’ll work hands-on with our earliest customers to embed Forgent AI into tender workflows and build the CS playbook from scratch.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a founding role: you’ll sit at the center of customers, product, and GTM, and you’ll help shape what we build next.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Own onboarding and time-to-value&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead structured onboarding for procurement/tender teams and cross-functional stakeholders (BD, legal, technical SMEs).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Map each customer’s tendering process and implement Forgent AI into it end-to-end. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive fast time-to-first-submission and repeatable rollout motions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Drive adoption, retention, and expansion&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build adoption plans and run QBRs/value reviews tied to measurable outcomes: hours saved, cycle-time reduction, tender throughput, compliance error reduction, and improved input to win rate. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own renewals and expansions in close collaboration with the leadership and sales.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-thread relationships (bid manager, procurement lead, compliance/legal, exec sponsor).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Be the customer voice in product&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate tender pain points into clear product requirements (e.g., form automation, compliance checks, discovery/matching). &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create feedback loops with Product/Engineering on AI quality, accuracy, compliance, and human-in-the-loop review workflows. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define “quality bars” for AI-generated tender responses (factuality, completeness, tone, locality, compliance).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Build the CS function from scratch&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create onboarding templates, success plans, customer health scoring, playbooks for risk/stalls, and escalation paths.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build enablement: training, best-practice guides, internal champions program.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop reference assets: case studies, lighthouse accounts, and proof points for GTM.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
