&lt;p&gt;We’re&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Cortea&lt;/strong&gt;, a Berlin-based startup building AI products that transform how audits get done.&lt;br&gt;Auditors spend too much time on manual, repetitive work. We’re fixing that by giving them AI tools that understand their workflows and eliminate the grind. Backed by top-tier VCs with €10m+ in funding, real customers, and a working product — now it’s time to scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We value&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;first-principles thinking, speed, trust, and kindness.&lt;/strong&gt; We work side by side in our Berlin office, moving fast and learning faster.&lt;/p&gt;
