&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Founding Software Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; London/onsite&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are building the &lt;strong&gt;Agentic Operating System for Consultants.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The $1 trillion consulting industry is powered by some of the world’s brightest minds, yet they remain trapped in manual, inefficient workflows - spreadsheet orchestration, slide-deck assembly, and fragmented data synthesis. We are moving the industry from &quot;human-plus-tools&quot; to &lt;strong&gt;autonomous agency.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Backed by a seed round from &lt;strong&gt;Cherry Ventures, Blue Lion&lt;/strong&gt;, and the founders of &lt;strong&gt;QuantumBlack&lt;/strong&gt;, our cap table includes angels from &lt;strong&gt;OpenAI, McKinsey, BCG, and Apple.&lt;/strong&gt; We have the capital, the network, and the domain expertise - now seeking further engineering support to get there faster.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Challenge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As one of our first engineers, you aren&#39;t just &quot;writing code&quot; - you are defining the technical DNA of the company. You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build Beyond the Chatbot:&lt;/strong&gt; Design multi-step agentic workflows that move past simple RAG into reliable, enterprise-grade inference.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architect for Scale &amp;amp; Privacy:&lt;/strong&gt; Build systems that can handle the rigorous data security requirements of Tier-1 financial and consulting firms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the Stack:&lt;/strong&gt; Make foundational decisions on everything from our LLM orchestration layer to our deployment infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interface with the Best:&lt;/strong&gt; Work directly with technical &amp;amp; non-technical stakeholders across clients &amp;amp; advisory teams (OpenAI/McKinsey vets) to translate elite consulting tradecraft into code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You Are a Fit If:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You are a Product Engineer:&lt;/strong&gt; You don’t need a 20-page PRD. You can take a vague user pain point from a design partner and ship a functional prototype by Friday.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have &quot;Velocity as a Habit&quot;:&lt;/strong&gt; You believe that in a seed-stage startup, speed is the only unfair advantage. You prefer shipping a 90% solution today over a perfect one next month.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You are &quot;T-Shaped&quot;:&lt;/strong&gt; You are deeply technical in Python/Typescript and LLM frameworks (PydanticAI, LangGraph, etc.), but you also care about UI polish and user ergonomics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have High Agency:&lt;/strong&gt; When you hit a wall with an undocumented API or a hallucinating model, you find a way around it, over it, or through it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Stack&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Languages:&lt;/strong&gt; Python, TypeScript&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI/Data:&lt;/strong&gt; Pydantic / LLM Frameworks, LiteLLM, ElasticSearch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Infra:&lt;/strong&gt; AWS, Terraform, PostgreSQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frontend:&lt;/strong&gt; React / Tailwind&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Us?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
